desc: ND Recycled Timber Furniture is a team of skilled craftsmen and artisans creating custom furniture in Melbourne, delivering Australia wide. Our furniture range includes cafe table tops, dining tables, coffee tables, bedding, entertainment units, board room tables and any custom furniture made to order, at your request.

layout.text: Continuing our close relationship with Endemol Shine Group we have constructed a table that is ideal for Channel 10’s hit show. The cleanly machined boards and sturdy timber ‘box end’ legs are finished with a clear stain that will hold up to even Gordon Ramsey’s sky high standards.
